@startuml detailed_simulation
title Cluster & Edit -- end-to-end mental simulation

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam defaultFontName "Helvetica"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam sequence {
    LifeLineBorderColor #888888
    ParticipantBorderColor #555555
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #F4F8FB
    ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
}

actor "User" as User
participant "Column menu\n(menu-edit-cells.js)" as Menu
participant "ClusteringDialog\n(clustering-dialog.js)" as Dialog
participant "ComputeClustersCommand\n(server)" as Cmd
participant "ClustererConfig\n(Jackson polymorphic)" as Config
participant "BinningClusterer\n/ kNNClusterer" as Clusterer
participant "KeyerFactory\n/ DistanceFactory" as Factory
participant "Engine + Project\n(filtered rows)" as Engine
participant "MassEditCommand\n+ MassEditOperation" as MassEdit

== 1. Open the dialog ==
User -> Menu : click "Edit cells -> Cluster and edit..."
Menu -> Dialog : new ClusteringDialog(column, "value")
Dialog -> Cmd : GET get-clustering-functions-and-distances
Cmd --> Dialog : { keyers: [...], distances: [...] }
Dialog --> User : show dialog (method, function, params)

== 2. Compute clusters ==
User -> Dialog : click "Cluster" (or auto-update)
Dialog -> Cmd : POST compute-clusters\nbody = { type, function, column, params }\n+ engine JSON + CSRF token
activate Cmd
Cmd -> Cmd : hasValidCSRFToken(request)?
Cmd -> Config : ParsingUtilities.mapper.readValue(\n  ClustererConfig.class)
note right of Config
  @JsonTypeInfo property = "type"
  type = "binning" -> BinningClustererConfig
  type = "knn"     -> kNNClustererConfig
end note
Config -> Factory : KeyerFactory.get("fingerprint")\nor DistanceFactory.get("levenshtein")
Factory --> Config : Keyer / SimilarityDistance instance
Config --> Cmd : Clusterer (initialized with column index)

Cmd -> Clusterer : computeClusters(engine)
activate Clusterer
Clusterer -> Engine : engine.getAllFilteredRows()
Engine --> Clusterer : FilteredRows
Clusterer -> Engine : filteredRows.accept(project, RowVisitor)
loop for each visible row
    Engine -> Clusterer : visit(project, rowIndex, row)
    alt binning
        Clusterer -> Clusterer : key = keyer.key(cellValue)\nbucket values by key
    else kNN
        Clusterer -> Clusterer : NGramClusterer.populate(value)
    end
end
Clusterer -> Clusterer : sort buckets, drop singletons
Clusterer --> Cmd : List<List<ClusteredEntry>>\n(JSON via @JsonValue)
deactivate Clusterer
Cmd --> Dialog : JSON response
deactivate Cmd

== 3. User reviews and edits ==
Dialog -> Dialog : _updateData(data)\nbuild facets (size, rowCount, avg, variance)
Dialog --> User : render table of clusters\n+ histogram facets
User -> Dialog : tick "Merge", choose new value\n(or click a suggested value)
User -> Dialog : click "Merge Selected & Re-Cluster"\nor "Merge Selected & Close"

== 4. Apply edits ==
Dialog -> Dialog : build edits = [{ from: [...], to: value }]
Dialog -> MassEdit : POST mass-edit\nbody = { columnName, expression, edits }
activate MassEdit
MassEdit -> MassEdit : new MassEditOperation(\n  engineConfig, columnName, expression, edits)
MassEdit -> Engine : create + apply Process\n(replaces matching cell values)
Engine -> Engine : write history entry (undo/redo)
MassEdit --> Dialog : ok
deactivate MassEdit
Dialog --> User : refresh data table\n(Re-Cluster runs step 2 again, Close dismisses)

@enduml
